0 0 800 400 re
f
GR
GS
[0.48 0 0 0.48 0 108.00001] CT
[1 0 0 1 0 0] CT
N
0 -225 M
1250 -225 L
1250 400 L
0 400 L
0 -225 L
cp
clip
GS
0 0 translate
800 400 scale
